components.HelloWorld: You've successfully created a project with {vite} + {vue}. What's next?

documentation.title: Documentation
documentation.message: Vue's {official} provides you with all information you need to get started.

tooling.title: tooling
tooling.message: This project is served and bundled with {vite}. The recommended IDE setup is {vscode} + {volar}. If you need to test your components and web pages, check out {cypress} and {testing}.{newline} More instructions are available in {readme}.

ecosystem.title: Ecosystem
ecosystem.message: Get official tools and libraries for your project: {state}, {router}, {test}, and {devtools}. If you need more resources, we suggest paying {awesome} a visit.

community.title: Community
community.message: Got stuck? Ask your question on {discord}, our official Discord server, or {stackoverflow}. You should also subscribe to {news} and follow the official {twitter} twitter account for latest news in the Vue world.

support.title: Support Vue
support.message: As an independent project, Vue relies on community backing for its sustainability. You can help us by {sponsor}.
